<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=9088&amp;p=96751#p96751"><![CDATA[
This is from my (C#) GB emu, originally based on code posted by Blarrg and passes his GB cpu tests.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">private void Daa&#40;&#41;<br />&#123;<br />    int a = _regs.A;<br /><br />    if &#40;!_regs.F.HasFlag&#40;Flags.N&#41;&#41;<br />    &#123;<br />        if &#40;_regs.F.HasFlag&#40;Flags.H&#41; || &#40;a &amp; 0xF&#41; &gt; 9&#41;<br />            a += 0x06;<br /><br />        if &#40;_regs.F.HasFlag&#40;Flags.C&#41; || a &gt; 0x9F&#41;<br />            a += 0x60;<br />    &#125;<br />    else<br />    &#123;<br />        if &#40;_regs.F.HasFlag&#40;Flags.H&#41;&#41;<br />            a = &#40;a - 6&#41; &amp; 0xFF;<br /><br />        if &#40;_regs.F.HasFlag&#40;Flags.C&#41;&#41;<br />            a -= 0x60;<br />    &#125;<br /><br />    _regs.F &amp;= ~&#40;Flags.H | Flags.Z&#41;;<br /><br />    if &#40;&#40;a &amp; 0x100&#41; == 0x100&#41;<br />        _regs.F |= Flags.C;<br /><br />    a &amp;= 0xFF;<br /><br />    if &#40;a == 0&#41;<br />        _regs.F |= Flags.Z;<br /><br />    _regs.A = &#40;byte&#41;a;<br />&#125;</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4497">DParrott</a> — Thu Jul 12, 2012 12:46 pm</p><hr />
